text: Leonid Fyodorov (25 March 1928 - 1993) was a Soviet ski jumper. He competed at the 1956 Winter Olympics and the 1960 Winter Olympics. ==References== Category:1928 births Category:1993 deaths Category:Soviet male ski jumpers Category:Soviet male Nordic combined skiers Category:Olympic ski jumpers of the Soviet Union Category:Olympic Nordic combined skiers of the Soviet Union Category:Ski jumpers at the 1960 Winter Olympics Category:Nordic combined skiers at the 1956 Winter Olympics Category:Nordic combined skiers at the 1960 Winter Olympics Category:Place of birth missing
